SYNOPSIS

    In your weaver.ini:

     [-SortSections]
     section=NAME
     section=VERSION
     section=SYNOPSIS
     section=DESCRIPTION
     ; put everything else here
     section=/./
     section=FUNCTIONS
     section=EXPORTS
     section=ATTRIBUTES
     section=METHODS
     section=ENVIRONMENT
     section=FILES
     section=HOMEPAGE
     section=SOURCE
     section=BUGS
     section=SEE ALSO
     section=AUTHOR
     section=COPYRIGHT AND LICENSE

DESCRIPTION

    This plugin lets you sort POD sections.

SEE ALSO

    Pod::Weaver::Role::SortSections

